  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - Got some dirt for you about the virus being part of their plan shit I mentioned
    before.
  - "Managed to brute force onto a government website through some exploit on the
    messages, couldn\u2019t get to the home page to view the rest of the site though. "
  - "We\u2019re thinking this whole town and everything in it is part of it aswell,
    no chance just this virus is the start and end of it all."
  - "All the while they probably barely made any fucking effort to look for the parents
    we lost, the family we lost, shaming anyone here who doesn\u2019t want to replace
    it by \u201Cmaking their own\u201D."
  - 'You: I see. Do you, want your own family though?'
  - "What and be another of the government\u2019s perfect little examples? Enough
    of those slaves lining the streets."
  - "Regardless , not a chance you\u2019d find anyone in here who\u2019d want to
    be a part of that family, just a waste of a thought."
  - "Anyways, that\u2019s all I\u2019ve got for now, I\u2019ll get back to you later."
